- Created .NET 10 API with EF Core + Npgsql (PostgreSQL)
- Entities: Applicant, ApplicantDocument, DocumentType, RecruitmentStage, RecruitmentNote, Quiz, QuizQuestion, QuizAttempt, QuizAnswer, TenantSettings
- Controllers: Auth, Applicant, Recruitment, Document, Quiz
